videos.description: Joel Berry II hits an early 3-pointer for North Carolina to put them up 11-3 on Wisconsin in the Maui Jim Maui Invitational Championship.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Berry hits the early three for UNC) 2016/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Berry hits the early three for UNC

videos.description: Nigel Hayes' first points are well worth the wait as he drives to the rim and rises for the two-handed slam in the first half against North Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wisconsin's Hayes attacks the rim with authority) 2016/11/23

videos.headline: Wisconsin's Hayes attacks the rim with authority

videos.description: Kennedy Meeks tacks on to the North Carolina lead with a layup and draws the foul, extending the Tar Heels' lead to 18 over Wisconsin after the free throw.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Meeks keeps powering through with and-1) 2016/11/23

videos.headline: Meeks keeps powering through with and-1

videos.description: North Carolina's Seventh Woods turns the ball over, but stays with the play and smashes Bronson Koenig's layup attempt against the backboard, as the Tar Heels lead big in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (UNC freshman emphatically blocks Wisconsin's Koenig) 2016/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: UNC freshman emphatically blocks Wisconsin's Koenig
